{"tid":211673,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"減緊肥/成功減到嘅同我入一入嚟","createTime":"2017-04-21T19:30:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T06:39:52.000Z","uid":72266,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"308b2b296a6239339c5231d23601f63f7af227f6","tid":211673,"uid":72266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:30:08.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲分享下心得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申175 80kg肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09889c3b31a26a125104bd08777fe80f6666c58e","tid":211673,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:32:42.000Z","msg":"食少d做運動<br />\n利申減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350af5f3da9e8e923d027ef59c0143632e5ab21b","tid":211673,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:49:41.000Z","msg":"其實第一步唔飲有糖既野一個月<br />\n已經會自動瘦左5kg"},{"pid":"156cde114048ca9f26a992c3f447321997e6a4f1","tid":211673,"uid":34148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T19:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實第一步唔飲有糖既野一個月<br />\n已經會自動瘦左5kg</blockquote><br />\n真，走糖走精緻澱粉即瘦，操埋肌唔會反彈tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69b2bfd658425d8f6bfbe995fcaca1ae625ed10","tid":211673,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:07:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實第一步唔飲有糖既野一個月<br />\n已經會自動瘦左5kg</blockquote><br />\n真，走糖走精緻澱粉即瘦，操埋肌唔會反彈tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前日日食飯都飲紙包檸檬茶<br />\n但戒咗之後又唔覺自己瘦左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問點樣減走個肚腩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胃腩冇乜，係肚臍下有舊肉凸咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要實實地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  滅落去似係肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到明明條腰都有d人魚線既 但舊腩就好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea97f44d1b0eb10a77fb9840723ebc8bf31f36c","tid":211673,"uid":21685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:18:43.000Z","msg":"其實肯郁既話，我覺得游水係最快既方法，其次係瑜珈同跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我減既時候無節食，淨係戒零食同凍飲<br />\n大概減咗半年，155lb減到120lb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"647361029806e60d82c344dc928021248a430b6c","tid":211673,"uid":16275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:25:22.000Z","msg":"曾經192減到132<br />\n但個排個人去到平台期<br />\n個人好辛苦好唔開心 去見營養師都係不斷喊<br />\n主要都係減少食量 多做運動 加上個排dse大壓力<br />\n而家肥返啲不過又再減緊<br />\n都係繼續多菜少肉夜晚戒澱粉質同喪做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"027f3144237b342553966ef76476d06fe2b43c7a","tid":211673,"uid":16275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:27:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>曾經192減到132<br />\n但個排個人去到平台期<br />\n個人好辛苦好唔開心 去見營養師都係不斷喊<br />\n主要都係減少食量 多做運動 加上個排dse大壓力<br />\n而家肥返啲不過又再減緊<br />\n都係繼續多菜少肉夜晚戒澱粉質同喪做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nPs 個彈最勁係一星期可以減4磅<br />\n諗返都覺得痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3376d35f46c886ca2239bcf9bade2d5a7a20258","tid":211673,"uid":86423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實第一步唔飲有糖既野一個月<br />\n已經會自動瘦左5kg</blockquote><br />\n真，走糖走精緻澱粉即瘦，操埋肌唔會反彈tim<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前日日食飯都飲紙包檸檬茶<br />\n但戒咗之後又唔覺自己瘦左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋想問點樣減走個肚腩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n胃腩冇乜，係肚臍下有舊肉凸咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要實實地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  滅落去似係肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到明明條腰都有d人魚線既 但舊腩就好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n戒左都唔代表你冇飲其它掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係減又想慳正係飲水就夠<br />\n我自己都係試過咁減<br />\n一個月先後磅重就輕左5kg到<br />\n但係又唔覺身型有瘦到<br />\n但係著衫或者著褲會feel到瘦左定肥左"},{"pid":"de14daefa91bc8d993f36a53eb6ad13d18ab79c9","tid":211673,"uid":51598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T20:49:30.000Z","msg":"岩岩食左包薯片<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847666cbd114b684b0a5de77743d57bbf546bd17","tid":211673,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T21:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食少d做運動<br />\n利申減緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇錯左少啲做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n心諗 咁點減啊"},{"pid":"d58737e5bdb05ecbe95dc2a59d0edf923c8eac30","tid":211673,"uid":83040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T00:16:29.000Z","msg":"我成功減到15磅 方法9點訓教"},{"pid":"3e6d6826c14873ee2c08fbdc4c38078801d83f6d","tid":211673,"uid":69599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成功減到15磅 方法9點訓教</blockquote><br />\n收嗲啦"},{"pid":"9db5384d44c52666714196e00844a555fda273a1"